      </a>
    </p>
    <!-- Introduction -->
    <p class="text-lg text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-300 2xl:text-xl mt-6 text-balance">
      A Chrome extension that allows users to control video playback speed using keyboard shortcuts.
      <br />
      <br />
      Built with vanilla JavaScript, published to Chrome Web Store.
    </p>
